## 3. Frontend Architecture

### 3.1 Pages (App Router)

| Route | Files | Description |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| `/` | `page.tsx` | Landing page — cinematic hero, 3D editor mockup, feature sections, footer. Has Sign Up + Log In nav links with `?mode=signup`/`?mode=login` query params |
| `/auth` | `AuthClient.tsx` | Login/signup form. Reads `?mode=` from URL. Has back link to landing. Redirects to `/dashboard` if authenticated |
| `/dashboard` | `DashboardClient.tsx` | Main dashboard — rooms list (owned/joined/public), search, filter tabs, create room modal, user avatar dropdown, real API data |
| `/room/[id]` | `RoomClient.tsx` | Room view — Monaco editor, real-time sync, chat, participants, share/settings modals, connection states |
| `/profile` | `ProfileClient.tsx` | User profile — avatar, name, email, join date, current plan stats, upgrade button |
| `/plans` | `PlansClient.tsx` | Pricing page — 3 tiers (Free $0, Pro $12, Premium $29), current plan highlighted |
| `/privacy` | `page.tsx` | Privacy policy (static) |
| `/terms` | `page.tsx` | Terms of service (static) |
| `/not-found` | `not-found.tsx`, `NotFoundClient.tsx` | Custom 404 page |

### 3.2 Components

| Component | File | Purpose |
|-----------|------|---------|
| `TopBar` | `TopBar.tsx` | Room header — back arrow, logo, room name, live badge, Download button, Share button, user avatar dropdown (Profile, Room Settings, Log out) |
| `Sidebar` | `Sidebar.tsx` | Dashboard sidebar — clickable logo (→ `/`), nav items: Rooms, Profile, Pricing, Settings (`#`), New Project button |
| `Modal` | `Modal.tsx` | Reusable modal — backdrop, title, children, optional footer |
| `Button` | `Button.tsx` | Styled button — variants: primary, ghost, outline. Sizes: sm, md, lg |
| `Input` | `Input.tsx` | Styled input with icon support |
| `RoomCard` | `RoomCard.tsx` | Room card for dashboard — gradient, name, language, member count, owner |
| `ParticipantAvatar` | `ParticipantAvatar.tsx` | Circular avatar with initials and color |
| `ChatMessage` | `ChatMessage.tsx` | Chat bubble with sender, time, message |
| `Logo` | `Logo.tsx` | CollabCode logo with icon |
| `Toggle` | `Toggle.tsx` | Toggle switch |
| `ProtectedRoute` | `ProtectedRoute.tsx` | Auth guard — redirects to `/auth` if not authenticated |
| `StatusBadge` | `StatusBadge.tsx` | Status indicator badge |
| `LanguageTag` | `LanguageTag.tsx` | Language label |
| `ConsoleOutput` | `ConsoleOutput.tsx` | Console/terminal output display |

### 3.3 API Client (`src/lib/api.ts`)

**Types exported:** `AuthTokens`, `UserProfile`, `Room`, `RoomOwner`, `DashboardData`, `RoomMember`, `InviteResult`, `ApiError`

**`authApi`:** `register`, `login`, `refresh`, `logout`, `logoutAll`, `getMe`
**`roomApi`:** `getDashboard`, `createRoom`, `getRoom`, `deleteRoom`, `joinRoom`, `createInvite`, `joinByInvite`, `getRoomMembers`, `removeMember`

All room methods require `accessToken` as first arg. Uses `credentials: "include"` for cookies.

### 3.4 Socket Client (`src/lib/socket/socketClient.ts`)

Exports `createRoomSocket(accessToken)` → typed Socket.IO client. Types exported: `Participant`, `ChatMessage`, `CursorUpdateEvent`, `CollabSocket`, all event payload types.

### 3.5 Hooks

**`useRoomSocket(roomId)`** — manages socket connection lifecycle. Returns:
- `document`, `version` — current doc state
- `participants` — `Participant[]` (userId + socketId only, no display names)
- `messages` — `ChatMessage[]`
- `cursors` — cursor positions
- `connectionStatus` — `"idle" | "connecting" | "connected" | "reconnecting" | "error"`
- `sendPatch(value)` — sends full doc + optimistic version increment
- `sendMessage(content)` — sends chat message
- `sendCursor({ line, ch })` — throttled cursor updates (75ms)

Constants: `MAX_PATCH_SIZE = 50KB`, `MAX_MESSAGE_LENGTH = 2000`, `CURSOR_THROTTLE_MS = 75`

### 3.6 Auth Context (`src/contexts/AuthContext.tsx`)

Provides: `accessToken`, `user` (UserProfile), `isLoading`, `isAuthenticated`, `login`, `register`, `logout`, `refreshAccessToken`

- Auto-refreshes on mount via cookie
- Periodic refresh every 13 minutes
- Fetches user profile after each token refresh

### 3.7 Design System

- **Colors:** `primary` = purple (#895af6), `background-dark` = near-black, `accent-dark` for hover states
- **Typography:** System font via Tailwind + JetBrains Mono for editor
- **Patterns:** `bg-[#0a0a0a]` cards, `border-white/5` borders, `text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest` labels, `backdrop-blur` effects
- **Animations:** `animate-pulse` for live indicator, `glow-primary` for buttons, `nav-glow` for active sidebar items

